reviews.title: Fast, Compact, and Classy
reviews.review_text: I've been using this Onn wall charger for a few weeks, and it's a solid addition to my gadget lineup. It has two ports‚Äîone standard USB-A and one USB-C for newer iPhones‚Äîand pushes out 32 W of power. It's not as beefy as my 120 W original Apple charger, but it still charges my iPhone to 100 % in about 30 minutes. The plastic shell wraps around all four sides, giving it a clean, elegant look, and the white finish feels classy. The foldable plug makes it easy to toss in a bag when I travel. The only downside is that it doesn't support higher wattage or Power Delivery required for laptops, but for everyday use, it's stylish and does the job well.

reviews.title: It works it's cute IPhone 11 and higher compatable
reviews.review_text: My old Apple charging cube was getting really hot and wasn't consistently charging my phone so I ordered this one and it arrived the next day. The fast and free shipping straight to my backdoor is an additional plus. I have an IPhone 11 that uses the USB 3 but should I upgrade my phone it'll charge it too! That's another plus! Oh, and it's cute!

reviews.title: Dual port for everything use
reviews.review_text: I received the ONN Dual Port USB C / USB wall charger to test in exchange for this review. The charger is really nice, I love the design and that it has ports for cables that I use on a daily basis. The charging speed is really good and it was easy to set up as it's plug and go. There is small light showing it's working which is great but I didn't notice it until I turned the charger right side up. Overall I'm really happy with the charger and would totally buy this again.

reviews.title: Loving It!
reviews.review_text: I've been using this ONN dual port USB-C/USB wall charger and I honestly love it. It charges my phone way faster than my other chargers, which is a huge win for me. The fast charge power delivery really makes a difference, and the LED power indicator is a nice touch so I always know it's working. It also has short circuit protection, which gives me peace of mind, and the design is sleek and travel-friendly. I really like the overall look and feel‚Äîit just feels like a high-quality charger. Definitely a great pick if you're looking for something reliable and fast!

reviews.review_text: I absolutely loved this dual port USB portable charger. It's honestly so great super small, lightweight, and incredibly convenient to take everywhere. reviews.title: Affordable & Efficient Dual-Port Charger
reviews.review_text: The onn Dual-Port USB-C / USB Fast Charging Wall Charger has proven to be a reliable addition to my charging setup. The charger features a 20W USB-C port with Power Delivery, allowing for fast charging of compatible devices. I can charge my phone up to 50% in about 30 minutes, which is quite convenient. The additional 12W USB-A port is handy for charging a second device simultaneously, though at a slower rate. One aspect I appreciate is its compact design, making it easy to carry around. However, I noticed that it doesn't have folding prongs, which would have been a nice feature for travel. Overall, for its price point, the Onn Dual-Port Charger offers solid performance and convenience. It's a great option for those looking for an affordable charger that can handle multiple devices.

reviews.title: Compact & Fast Charging
reviews.review_text: This was exactly what I needed but didn't know it: even with the charging station in the video it made it difficult as it's not very portable even from room to room. I work from home so I am often charging multiple devices at once & they are different types of USBs. Dragging that station from room to room was annoying & this is perfect for toting around the house or for an outing or vacation. It's super lightweight, no assembly is required & it charges both devices at the same time so quickly! I am really thrilled with this product. I don't know how long it will hold up but I am hoping it does & if it doesn't this is absolutely something I would purchase again. I absolutely recommend this!

reviews.title: Great USB charger
reviews.review_text: This dual-port USB charger is great! I like the look and feel of it and find the USB/USB-C double ports very convenient. I also like how the plug folds in on itself for easy packing, and the charging indicator light is very handy. It is a bit bulky and large for a charger block so I probably wouldn't reach for this when traveling light, but it is a great option around the house and has powered my devices quickly and reliably so far.

reviews.title: Onn wall Charger
reviews.review_text: I absolutely love the pink Onn Dual-Port USB-C / USB Fast Charging Wall Charger. The color is so cute! It adds a fun pop to my desk and travel bag, plus my teenage boys & husband won't touch it because it's pink. More importantly, it charges my devices really fast. The USB-C port powers up my phone in no time, and I can charge my earbuds at the same time using the regular USB port. I highly recommend!

reviews.title: Great Travel Charger!
reviews.review_text: I am quickly becoming a huge fan of Onn products and this travel charger is one of the reasons why. I love that it has the two different ports and I also love that the plug folds down for ease of packing. It's well made and very sturdy. I am very impressed with the "fast charge" and feel that is accurate. The only thing, and it could be just me misunderstanding the wording on the package, is the LED lighting. I tried it in different lighting and didn't see an LED light anywhere. That said, I don't care at all about that (I don't need a nightlight in my hotel room), so I'm not going to reduce my overall rating for that. It could easily be a fault in this unit that doesn't have any bearing on how it functions and honestly, I'm happier without the light. It has been a great charger and it is currently in my travel bag awaiting a trip this weekend!
